    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to people in Spain and Latin America who work with sacred art and the carving of retables. Because of their drawing skills they were also known historically as “professors of architecture.”</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
